<title>Chisʋs puyulla ka ƲIT108</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Chisʋs puyulla ka
 Kiloh anukfilli;
 Ilap nipi, im issish aiena,
 Ishit pi chukumpa tok.

[V2]
 Ilap haknip oka
 Pʋska itapesʋt,
 Oh ʋpá, hʋchin
 tushtoa hatok,
 Pi̱ kanʋt ahanchishke.

[V3]
 Im issish atukma
 Wain* a̱ itapesʋt,
 Oh ishkó, hʋchi̱
 hlatahampa tok,
 Pi̱ hullot ahanchishke

[B1]
   *Oka pa̱ki

[V4]
 Oh ʋpá, oh ishkó,
 A̱hli hosh a̱ yimmit
 Ʋpakmʋt, ishkokmʋt okcha̱ya na
 Bilia he, achishke.

[V5]
 Pʋshka e pa, wain ma
 Il ishko kʋt, Chisʋs
 Illi tok a̱, ik pimi hakso ho̱,
 Ʋla he, apesa tok.

[V6]
 Chisʋs ʋt pi̱ hullo;
 Kiloh ithaiyana;
 Kiloh im aia̱hlit, a̱hlit, a̱hlit
 Eho holitoblashke.

[V7]
 Klaist ʋt achukmʋshke;
 Kiloh aiokpʋchi;
 Chu̱kʋsh isht ai a̱hli
 pullʋt, pullʋt
 Iloh im antiashke.</lyrics>
<aka>Sacramental</aka>
</song>